{"id": "6977", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6977", "title": "Athena's Wrath", "text": "Athena's Wrath is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Battle%20Scythe\"&gt;Battle Scythe&lt;/a&gt; from \"\".\nAkin to fellow unique &lt;a href=\"Polearms\"&gt;polearm&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Blackleach%20Blade\"&gt;Blackleach Blade&lt;/a&gt;, Athena's Wrath boasts a high Maximum Damage that increases with level. However, instead of bestowing &lt;a href=\"Life\"&gt;Life&lt;/a&gt; leech, it gives a boost to life directly. As indicated by its skill bonuses, Athena's Wrath is directed towards &lt;a href=\"Druid\"&gt;Druid&lt;/a&gt; use.\nStats.\nTwo-Hand Damage: (45-50) To (113-224) \nRequired Level: 42\nRequired Strength: 82\nRequired Dexterity: 82\nDurability: 65\nPolearm Class - "}
