{"id": "34182", "revid": "25771421", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=34182", "title": "Augustine's Panacea", "text": "Augustine's Panacea are a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"quivers\"&gt;quiver&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href=\"Demon%20Hunter\"&gt;Demon Hunter&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 50 to drop. In patch 2.4.1, it replaced the &lt;a href=\"Meticulous%20Bolts\"&gt;Meticulous Bolts&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe unique affix affects each rune of the &lt;a href=\"Elemental%20Arrow\"&gt;Elemental Arrow&lt;/a&gt; differently. Ball Lightning essentially zaps each target more times before it travels too far from it (total distance it covers does not change). Other runes get multiplicative increases in damage and secondary effects."}
