{"id": "16827", "revid": "845641", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16827", "title": "Aztuhl", "text": "Captain Aztuhl was the captain of a band of mercenaries in the employment of the merchant Mastetr &lt;a href=\"Fahin\"&gt;Fahin&lt;/a&gt;. Fahin had taken Aztuhl into his home when he was a young boy and adopted him as his own son. Aztuhl considered Fahin his father.\nAztuhl was killed during the ambush by &lt;a href=\"Zorun%20Tzin\"&gt;Zorun Tzin&lt;/a&gt;. "}
