{"id": "24718", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24718", "title": "Azurewrath", "text": "Azurewrath is an &lt;a href=\"angel\"&gt;angel&lt;/a&gt;ic &lt;a href=\"runeblade\"&gt;runeblade&lt;/a&gt; once wielded by the &lt;a href=\"angel\"&gt;angel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Izual\"&gt;Izual&lt;/a&gt;.\nLore.\nBlessed by the &lt;a href=\"Lightsong\"&gt;Song of the Arch&lt;/a&gt; to be an instrument of the righteous, Azurewrath was wielded by Izual. He utilized it in the &lt;a href=\"Fifth%20Battle%20of%20the%20Diamond%20Gates\"&gt;Fifth Battle of the Diamond Gates&lt;/a&gt;, and to best knowledge, during his failed assault on the &lt;a href=\"Hellforge\"&gt;Hellforge&lt;/a&gt;. While Izual was corrupted by &lt;a href=\"Burning%20Hells\"&gt;Hell&lt;/a&gt;, Azurewrath was spared the corruption that consumed its master.\nIn-game.\nAzurewrath may be found in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\", \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\", and \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\":"}
{"id": "1924", "revid": "53848336", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1924", "title": "Azurewrath (Diablo II)", "text": "Azurewrath is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Phase%20Blade\"&gt;Phase Blade&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nPerhaps an improved version of its sister Phase Blade, , Azurewrath has properties along similar lines.\nBoasting both an extremely high added &lt;a href=\"Cold\"&gt;Cold&lt;/a&gt; damage and also an added &lt;a href=\"magic%20damage\"&gt;magic damage&lt;/a&gt;, Azurewrath can do tons of damage even if an enemy is immune to cold. \nAzurewrath also gives its wielder a &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary%20%28skill%29\"&gt;Sanctuary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"aura\"&gt;aura&lt;/a&gt;. This makes it particularly effective against &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; enemies. Like most aura gear, Azurewrath is &lt;a href=\"ladder\"&gt;ladder&lt;/a&gt; only. \nLore.\n&lt;a href=\"Azurewrath\"&gt;Azurewrath&lt;/a&gt; was created by the Archangel &lt;a href=\"Tyrael\"&gt;Tyrael&lt;/a&gt;. It was wielded by &lt;a href=\"Izual\"&gt;Izual&lt;/a&gt;, one of Tyrael's lieutenants, during an ill-fated assault on the &lt;a href=\"Hellforge\"&gt;Hellforge&lt;/a&gt; to delay the forging of the demonblade &lt;a href=\"Shadowfang\"&gt;Shadowfang&lt;/a&gt;.\nStats.\nOne-Hand Damage: \nRequired Level: 85\nRequired Strength: 25\nRequired Dexterity: 136\nSword Class - "}
{"id": "21173", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21173", "title": "Azurewrath (Diablo III)", "text": "Azurewrath is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"sword\"&gt;sword&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 60 to drop.\nIt is one of the two one-handed weapons in game (the other being &lt;a href=\"Utar%27s%20Roar\"&gt;Utar's Roar&lt;/a&gt;) that can have a bonus damage to &lt;a href=\"Cold\"&gt;Cold&lt;/a&gt; skills. \nAzurewrath also radiates angelic light deadly for &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Demons\"&gt;Demons&lt;/a&gt; (mirroring the \"Diablo II\" counterpart with &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary%20%28Skill%29\"&gt;Sanctuary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Aura\"&gt;Aura&lt;/a&gt;), and also has a high chance to &lt;a href=\"Freeze\"&gt;Freeze&lt;/a&gt; an enemy upon hitting."}
