{"id": "6014", "revid": "47915220", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6014", "title": "Balrog (Diablo I)", "text": "Balrogs are most commonly found in the Hell levels of the original \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20%28Game%29\"&gt;Diablo&lt;/a&gt;\", except for 16. They are the toughest of the Balrog groups.\nThey wield s, and can breathe fire (the animation mimics that of the &lt;a href=\"Inferno%20%28Diablo%20I%20Spell%29\"&gt;Inferno&lt;/a&gt; spell). Avoid them if they are in groups, for several swings with their swords deal heavy damage and are devastating if one were to be low on &lt;a href=\"Defense\"&gt;armor class&lt;/a&gt;."}
