{"id": "33132", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=33132", "title": "Band of Might", "text": "Band of Might is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"rings\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\", added in patch 2.4 (replacing &lt;a href=\"Stolen%20Ring\"&gt;Stolen Ring&lt;/a&gt;). It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 8 to drop.\nThe unique affix effect does not stack, but is multiplicative to other similar effects. The damage reduction applies the moment cast is performed, even if it does not hit anything."}
