{"id": "41803", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41803", "title": "Bartender Bailey", "text": "Bartender Bailey serves in the &lt;a href=\"Wolf%20City%20Tavern\"&gt;Wolf City Tavern&lt;/a&gt;, and is a member of the &lt;a href=\"Shadows\"&gt;Shadows&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt;, he was approached by &lt;a href=\"the%20Shard-seeker\"&gt;the Shard-seeker&lt;/a&gt;, seeking passage to &lt;a href=\"Kehjistan\"&gt;Kehjistan&lt;/a&gt;. He directed them to &lt;a href=\"Captain%20Rehm\"&gt;Captain Rehm&lt;/a&gt;, who was just outside the tavern, brawling with pirates. He told them to hop to it, not wanting the brawl to come inside the tavern.\nC. &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231273\"&gt;1273&lt;/a&gt;, he made an order to &lt;a href=\"Charsi\"&gt;Charsi&lt;/a&gt; for 60 pewter flagons.\nIn-game.\nBailey is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". found in the Wolf City Tavern. Talking to him ends the \"&lt;a href=\"Answers%20in%20the%20East\"&gt;Answers in the East&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt;, and initiates \"&lt;a href=\"A%20Captain%27s%20Need\"&gt;A Captain's Need&lt;/a&gt;.\"\nBailey hands out &lt;a href=\"Contracts\"&gt;Contracts&lt;/a&gt; to players.\nDevelopment.\nIn the game's beta, he was simply called \"Bartender.\""}
