{"id": "21435", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21435", "title": "Bastion's Revered", "text": "Bastion's Revered is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Two-Handed%20Mighty%20Weapons\"&gt;two-handed mighty weapon&lt;/a&gt; for the in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 29 to drop.\nThe unique affix essentially doubles the maximum &lt;a href=\"Attack%20Speed\"&gt;Attack Speed&lt;/a&gt; bonus of ; with the Maniac or Vanguard rune, it will double the damage and speed bonuses as well.\nAs of patch 2.6.8, it gained an additional effect that basically allows hitting up to 10 enemies within 15 yards of the target at once. The main target will still take full damage, except for the share of the extra hit, while the total damage done to other foes will always be fixed. Damage and maximum amount of hits per cast will scale with the amount of stacks."}
