{"id": "50754", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50754", "title": "Slam (monster skill)", "text": "Slam is a skill commonly used by &lt;a href=\"boss\"&gt;boss&lt;/a&gt;es in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". The boss raises their arms/&lt;a href=\"weapon\"&gt;weapon&lt;/a&gt; above their head, then slams it to the ground causing &lt;a href=\"knockback\"&gt;loss of control&lt;/a&gt; and/or &lt;a href=\"stun\"&gt;stun&lt;/a&gt;. This attack can also cause an explosion or, for bosses with &lt;a href=\"fire\"&gt;fire&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"cold\"&gt;cold&lt;/a&gt; damage, have a chance to leave the ground scorched or frosted. This skill is used by &lt;a href=\"Anguish%20Harvester\"&gt;Anguish Harvester&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Rock%20Golem\"&gt;Rock&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=\"Sand%20Golem\"&gt;Sand Golem&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Agronix\"&gt;Agronix&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Cold%20Snap\"&gt;Cold Snap&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Skeleton%20King\"&gt;Skeleton King&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Izilech%20the%20Misshapen\"&gt;Izilech the Misshapen&lt;/a&gt;."}
