{"id": "6298", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6298", "title": "Seraph's Hymn", "text": "Seraph's Hymn is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Amulets\"&gt;amulet&lt;/a&gt; from \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nThe unique amulet of choice for a &lt;a href=\"Paladin\"&gt;Paladin&lt;/a&gt; specializing in &lt;a href=\"Defensive%20Auras\"&gt;Defensive Auras&lt;/a&gt;, Seraph's Hymn gives a large skill boost accordingly. A character utilizing Seraph's Hymn will be effective against both &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Demons\"&gt;Demons&lt;/a&gt;, although no more effective against &lt;a href=\"Animals\"&gt;Animals&lt;/a&gt;.\nStats.\nRequired Level: 65"}
