s:\n&lt;a href=\"Witch%20Doctor\"&gt;Witch Doctor&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Helltooth%20Harness\"&gt;Helltooth Harness&lt;/a&gt;.\nTips:\n&lt;a href=\"Raiment%20of%20the%20Jade%20Harvester\"&gt;Raiment of the Jade Harvester&lt;/a&gt;.\nTips:\n&lt;a href=\"Spirit%20of%20Arachyr\"&gt;Spirit of Arachyr&lt;/a&gt;.\nTips:\n&lt;a href=\"Zunimassa%27s%20Haunt\"&gt;Zunimassa's Haunt&lt;/a&gt;.\nTips:\n&lt;a href=\"Wizard\"&gt;Wizard&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Delsere%27s%20Magnum%20Opus\"&gt;Delsere's Magnum Opus&lt;/a&gt;.\nTips:\n&lt;a href=\"Firebird%27s%20Finery\"&gt;Firebird's Finery&lt;/a&gt;.\nTips:\n&lt;a href=\"Tal%20Rasha%27s%20Elements\"&gt;Tal Rasha's Elements&lt;/a&gt;.\nTips:\n&lt;a href=\"Vyr%27s%20Amazing%20Arcana\"&gt;Vyr's Amazing Arcana&lt;/a&gt;.\nTips:"}
