{"id": "42083", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=42083", "title": "Shayeed the Fallen", "text": "Shayeed was a knight in the &lt;a href=\"Order%20of%20Light\"&gt;Order of Light&lt;/a&gt;, and friend to &lt;a href=\"Lachdanan\"&gt;Lachdanan&lt;/a&gt;. After they returned from the disastarous war against &lt;a href=\"Westmarch\"&gt;Westmarch&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Lachdanan\"&gt;Lachdanan&lt;/a&gt; and many of his knights turned against &lt;a href=\"Leoric\"&gt;Leoric&lt;/a&gt;, who was clearly mad. However, Shayeed chose loyalty to his king, and was killed by Lachdanan in the ensuing battle. Afterwards, he lay his friend to rest.\nShayeed's &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;spirit&lt;/a&gt; remained tethered to &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary\"&gt;Sanctuary&lt;/a&gt;, seething with rage. However, a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;hero/group of heroes&lt;/a&gt; summoned his spirit in &lt;a href=\"Ashwold%20Cemetery\"&gt;Ashwold Cemetery&lt;/a&gt;, and removed his tether to the mortal realm.\nIn-game.\nShayeed the Fallen is encountered in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". He is the target of the \"&lt;a href=\"Fallen%20Warrior\"&gt;Fallen Warrior&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Ashwold%20Cemetery\"&gt;Ashwold Cemetery&lt;/a&gt;. Specifically, he is found in &lt;a href=\"Silent%20Overlook\"&gt;Silent Overlook&lt;/a&gt;, where players must find the \"Tomb of Shayeed.\" In truth, one just needs to find his gravestone and tap on it to trigger the encounter.\nShayeed is a &lt;a href=\"Super%20Unique\"&gt;Super Unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Royal%20Guard%20%28Monster%29\"&gt;Royal Guard&lt;/a&gt;. He has a shield-ram attack, can drop a roating laser, and call lightning bolts down. He is immune to &lt;a href=\"knockback\"&gt;knockback&lt;/a&gt;."}
