{"id": "51246", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=51246", "title": "Shelter of Khalim", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"armor\"&gt;armor&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". When equipped, it enables the player to use a variant of &lt;a href=\"Conjuration%20of%20Light\"&gt;Conjuration of Light&lt;/a&gt;."}
