{"id": "26247", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26247", "title": "Shi Mizu's Haori", "text": "Shi Mizu's Haori\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Body%20Armor\"&gt;chest armor&lt;/a&gt; in\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;. It requires\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a031 to drop.\nWhen seriously injured, it raises &lt;a href=\"Critical%20Hit\"&gt;Critical Hit&lt;/a&gt; chance to 100%. &lt;a href=\"Build\"&gt;Build&lt;/a&gt;s using this item tend to utilize a great deal of &lt;a href=\"Toughness\"&gt;Toughness&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"absorption\"&gt;absorption&lt;/a&gt; shields without any &lt;a href=\"healing\"&gt;healing&lt;/a&gt; to keep their &lt;a href=\"Life\"&gt;Life&lt;/a&gt; total below the threshold without being at immediate risk of &lt;a href=\"death\"&gt;death&lt;/a&gt;. This threshold is more difficult to maintain during later &lt;a href=\"Season\"&gt;Season&lt;/a&gt;s in which the &lt;a href=\"Altar%20of%20Rites\"&gt;Altar of Rites&lt;/a&gt; encourages frequent &lt;a href=\"potion\"&gt;potion&lt;/a&gt; use.\nThis chest piece has a unique look on the hero, rather than using a re-painted model of a normal armor."}
{"id": "4850", "revid": "839260", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4850", "title": "Shield", "text": ""}
{"id": "24499", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24499", "title": "Shield Bash", "text": "Shield Bash is a Secondary\u00a0 skill, closely resembling the &lt;a href=\"Paladin\"&gt;Paladin&lt;/a&gt; skills &lt;a href=\"Smite\"&gt;Smite&lt;/a&gt; and\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Charge\"&gt;Charge&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nThe Crusader rushes forward with +140% increased speed (only if directed at the target, not at the location), up to 80 yards. While charging, the Crusader moves unhindered and can move through enemies (not obstacles), until they reach a designated target. Then the charge hits one enemy (and all others within 3 yards of the target and 20 yards behind the target; the cone is much broader than the visual effect) for 700% damage plus the shield's Block Chance x 3 (that is, up to 60% additional damage as Holy, to a total of 760%, for most level 70 shields; other block chance increasing modifiers, if any, work too). Primary target is also always &lt;a href=\"Immobilize\"&gt;Immobilize&lt;/a&gt;d for 1 second if the Crusader has charged into them.\nTargeting an empty ground will retarget charge to the closest enemy within 10 yards or, if none found, the Crusader will unleash the Bash right in front of themselves. The ability can be interrupted during the hit animation, and some other skills can be used at that time."}
