{"id": "24518", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24518", "title": "Shield Glare", "text": "Shield Glare is a Defensive skill.\nIn-game.\nAffected enemies are Blinded. Unlike the &lt;a href=\"Monk\"&gt;Monk&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"Blinding%20Flash\"&gt;Blinding Flash&lt;/a&gt;, enemies immune or resistant to Blind do not have chance to miss, but in return, &lt;a href=\"elites\"&gt;elites&lt;/a&gt; are affected in the same way as lesser enemies. Hits a broad cone in front of the Crusader, roughly 120 degrees wide. Like all Blind effects, it works on &lt;a href=\"Bosses\"&gt;Bosses&lt;/a&gt;, and the secondary effects still occur even if the target is immune to Blind."}
